title: What Makes Us Weird
description: Let's face it, we're weird and we know it. One of us can't put her left shoe on first without crying and the other has a history of rocking pleather pants and platform heels. Guess who? Visit us at Patreon.com/Homemakerchicpodcast to be fabulously "homemaker chic"!
